caption.title: Titration of the viral particles of CHIKV, DENV and ZIKV in body and saliva of AR wP and AR wP-M Ae. Albopictus.
caption.p: The number of viral particles in the body and saliva of both mosquito lines were titrated for evaluating the viral load in each mosquito line. A: the number of CHIKV viral particles in the body and saliva of AR wP and AR wP-M at 7 and 14 dpi; B and C: the number of DENV-1 (B) and ZIKV (C) viral particles in the body and saliva of AR wP and AR wP-M at 14 and 21 dpi. Differences between Ae. albopictus lines were not statistically significant (Kruskalâ€“Wallis test: P > 0.05).
